--------------------------------------------------
CVA Silicon Technologies        
    Hardware Development Repository 
--------------------------------------------------

Git Repository Directory Structure:
   |-simu
   |-source
   |---design
   |---verif
   |-synth

Important Commands
- ./simu.sh <topmodule_name>                                             // For simulation using xcelium
- genus -f synth_genus.tcl -execute "set design_name <topmodule_name>"   // For synthesis using xcelium

- ./simu_icarus.sh <topmodule_name>                                      // For simulation using icarus
- chmod +x run_synth.sh                                                  // For synthesis
- ./run_synth.sh <topmodule_name>                                        // using yosys


Dependencies
- Icarus Verilog for simulation 
- GTKWave for wave debug
- Yosis for logic synthesis
- SKY130 PDK 
